library(readr)

chocolates <- 
  read_csv(
    "https://dqlab-dataset.s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/chocolates.csv",
    col_types = cols(
      panelist = col_factor(),
      session = col_factor(),
      rank = col_factor(),
      product = col_factor(levels = paste0("choc", 1:6)),
      .default = col_integer()
    )
  )
